# direction: right

User: User {
  shape: person
}

CLI: agent.py (CLI interface) {
  shape: rectangle
  style: { fill: "#f4f4f4" }
}

Agent_Core: Deep Agent System {
  shape: package
  style: { fill: "#e1f5fe" }

  Planner: write_todos tool
  Toolkit: SQLDatabaseToolkit
  Memory: FilesystemBackend
}

LLM: ChatOllama\n(gemma4:e2b) {
  shape: rectangle
  style: { fill: "#e8f5e9" }
}

Database: chinook.db\n(SQLite) {
  shape: cylinder
  style: { fill: "#fff3e0" }
}

Prompts: AGENTS.md &\nSKILL.md {
  shape: document
}

# The Execution Flow
User -> CLI: 1. Asks Natural Language Question
CLI -> Agent_Core: 2. Parses Args & Invokes Agent

Prompts -> Agent_Core: Loads Guardrails/Instructions
Agent_Core -> LLM: Connects to Local Model (Temp=0)

Agent_Core.Planner -> LLM: 3. Formulates Step-by-Step Plan
Agent_Core.Toolkit -> Database: 4. Introspects Schema (sql_db_schema)
Database -> Agent_Core.Toolkit: Returns Tables/Columns

Agent_Core.Toolkit -> Database: 5. Executes SQL (sql_db_query)
Database -> Agent_Core.Toolkit: Returns Data Rows

Agent_Core.Memory -> Agent_Core.Memory: 6. Caches Intermediate Results

Agent_Core -> LLM: 7. Passes Data for Synthesis
LLM -> Agent_Core: Returns Natural Language Answer

Agent_Core -> CLI: 8. Yields Final Answer & Logprobs
CLI -> User: 9. Displays Formatted Rich Output